\section*{Prevention}

It focuses on the following areas:-
- Lifestyle- smoking cessation and moderation of alcohol intake.
- Exercise- achieving a higher peak bone mass through exercise.
- Nutrition- proper nutrition includes a diet sufficient in calcium and vitamin D- is necessary for calcium absorption and for normal bone mineralization.

